          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/29638166-from-sand-and-ash">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2280602906" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2503163755045008732"><i>
  <b>&quot;It was love that made each touch feel like redemption and each kiss like rebirth. Not just lust. Not just pleasure. It was love that created joy.&quot;</b>
</i><br/><br/>Ahhhh this book!!! I LOVED it so much. ❤❤❤<br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1437482947ra/15588641.gif' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
